OL,6,FLauren Bolton from Rossendale has been
OL,7,Ftold by a local businessman who
OL,8,Fwatched her story on the programme
OL,9,Fthat he will make up the #95,000
OL,10,Fneeded if they can reach half that
OL,11,Ftarget.
OL,13,FLauren lives in constant pain and is
OL,14,Funable to eat solid food and her
OL,15,Ffamily fear her health will continue
OL,16,Fto deteriorate without urgent surgery.
OL,18,FThe 29-year-old's family set up a in
OL,19,Fthe hope of raising the money for
OL,20,Fprivate surgery to replace her jaw
OL,21,Fjoint.
