OL,6,FAfter describing the impact of the ,
OL,7,Fshe watched as donations increased to
OL,8,Fthe target of #55,000.
OL,10,FLauren said: "I'm just blown away with
OL,11,Feveryone's kindness. Everyone who
OL,12,Fshared, everyone who's messaged. I've
OL,13,Fread those messages more than once."
OL,15,FNow, a local businessman has reached
OL,16,Fout to Lauren's father, Paul Bolton,
OL,17,Fto help.
OL,19,FPaul said: "He just said they'd sat
OL,20,Fthere and watched it and he said he
OL,21,Fwas really touched by our story.
