OL,3,CMystery businessman offers to pay for
OL,4,Chalf of woman's life-saving surgery
OL,6,F"He just said to his wife, 'We need to
OL,7,Fhelp that lass'."
OL,9,FThe businessman, who wishes to remain
OL,10,Fanonymous, has promised that if
OL,11,FLauren's fundraiser reaches #55,000 he
OL,12,Fwill pay the remainder of the fees.
OL,14,FPaul said: "I just want to give him a
OL,15,Fbig cuddle. He reminds me of my
OL,16,FGrandad. Just a lovely, lovely, bloke."
OL,18,FLauren has late stage (TMD) which has
OL,19,Fdamaged her jaw joint and her only
OL,20,Foption is a full replacement.
