OL,6,FBut it is a procedure so complex, only
OL,7,Fa handful of surgeons can do it and
OL,8,Fmost are private.
OL,10,FOn the NHS Lauren is looking at a wait
OL,11,Fof almost four years for the surgery.
OL,12,Fwhich her family fear she will not
OL,13,Fsurvive and are worried about the
OL,14,Fimpact of her weight loss on her
OL,15,Forgans.
OL,17,FNow, a possible end to Lauren's
OL,18,Fsuffering is in sight.
