OL,6,FOne viewer, Sue Cook from Congleton,
OL,7,Fwanted to help Lauren but was unable
OL,8,Fto donate to the online fundraiser.
OL,10,FInstead, she sent a #10 cheque to
OL,11,FRawtenstall's post office, hoping they
OL,12,Fcould get it to Lauren.
OL,14,FAlong with the cheque was a letter,
OL,15,Fwhich reads: "Wish it could be more...
OL,16,FHowever I hope it everyone watching
OL,17,Fwill donate to get you the operation
OL,18,Fyou need."
